Version 1.15-unreleased
=======================

* fixed bug #15223 (`https://gna.org/bugs/?15223'): the coverability graph is
  now not used in the `HOME' mode

* added an experimental parameter `-r' to write all analysis results into a
  single file in the file format of libconfig (see
  `http://www.hyperrealm.com/libconfig')

* fixed bug #12910 (`https://gna.org/bugs/?12910'): file output for `-g' and
  `-m' parameter was broken


See file ChangeLog <http://service-technology.org/files/lola/ChangeLog> for
complete version history.

